  },
  "scope": "Single Windows/MSVC machine, one-million-cell 10-column numeric, mixed-inline and formula plus external-hyperlink sources, 1000 targeted upserts, source DEFLATE level 6 and recorded output levels only. Office was not run. No cross-machine, arbitrary-workbook, pure-encoder, backend-superiority or OpenXLSX-superiority claim."
